@63   = ~My closest of kin are my parents, Ulguth and Mara, a brother, Gotom, and a sister, Elina. I am the youngest of four. I had an older brother, Envin, but he died from a disease when I was five.~
@64   = ~We are a merchant family, and my father is a hard working trader. He specializes in beast-taming and breeding, which are done mostly on our country estate south of the city.~
@65   = ~My mother has a special hobby. She is a very fine cook of exotic meats. She has won prizes with her recipes.~
