@268  = ~I had a dream last night... No, no nightmare. Don't look so worried! It was about you. (smile)~
@269  = ~(You take a look at your ring...)~
@270  = ~Tell me something about Helm or the Order, Ajantis.~
@271  = ~To do *what*? Honestly, love, I don't like what kind of game you are making out of this.~
@272  = ~No.~
@273  = ~(sigh)~
