@662  = ~However, we do not have time to go there now, Ajantis.~
@663  = ~Well, so it shall be. We will go to the Mithrest Inn in Waukeen's Promenade once we reach Athkatla.~
@664  = ~Even if we could get there from here, we wouldn't have the time to go to the shop, Ajantis.~
