@681  = ~(sigh) If need be...~
@682  = ~That is not a problem. There is the possibility of having sample rings sent for us to inspect. I will send master Surianko a message as soon as possible, telling him that we wish this. If our obligations should leave us the time to stop by his shop, then we can gladly do so.~
@683  = ~I thank you. Let me quickly take measurements with this piece of string...~
@684  = ~I am sorry if it is uncomfortable for you, but I do not want to risk mistakes. I thank you. Let me quickly take measurements with this piece of string...~
@685  = ~It is a miracle, how tender and nevertheless strong your finger is, <CHARNAME>... what beautiful, fine fingers you have. These extremely delicate joints...~
@686  = ~(embarrassed coughing) I... I should perhaps let go of your hand again.~
@687  = ~Not without a kiss for me from my very charming admirer.~
